        <p class="text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-4">You've made it to the 12-month mark.</p>
        <div class="inline-block bg-frangipani/10 border border-frangipani px-6 py-3">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-carbon">Status: Refresh Unlocked (Free)</p>
