              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Lian goes into the code. We don't just change text; we can update the layout, swap the hero images, and modernize the feel to match where your business is <em>now</em>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-10 border-l-4 border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
